videos.description: Steph Curry drains a very deep 3-pointer and drives past everyone on the Thunder for the lay-in, finishing the first quarter with 24 points.

videos.description: Steph Curry gets the ball in transition and uses a retreat dribble to back away from the 3-point line to pull up and hit an even deeper shot against the sideline.
